FY24 CLUSTER TALENTS
CHILD PROTECTION CODE OF CONDUCT
I promise to strictly follow the rules and guidelines in this code of conduct as a condition to my engagement in this Kilifi-Ganze-Kaloleni Cluster events.
I WILL:
1.	Treat everyone with respect, patience, integrity, courtesy, dignity and consideration.
2.	Never be alone with children and/ or youth at the festivals without notifying my project worker.
3.	Maintain appropriate physical boundaries at all times and touch children or my fellow youths when necessary â€“only in ways that are appropriate, public and non-sexual.
4.	Comply with the mandatory reporting regulations of my project.
5.	Report suspected cases of child abuse.
6.	Cooperate fully in any investigation of abuse of children and/or youth.
